---

# 9. Output Structure

After execution, outputs will be generated in:

```
outputs/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ metrics/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ predictions/
в””в”Ђв”Ђ generated_code/
```

---

# Notes

вЂў Ensure **Ollama is running** before executing the pipeline.
вЂў The script automatically detects the Ollama binary if installed in standard locations.
вЂў Models are downloaded locally and run **offline after installation**.

